reviews: Great fit, hubby likes it. Material is thick but it does breathe. Good for men who sweat quite a bit I think. Not as soft as I had expected. After one wash with good mild detergent in cold water it has faded quite a bit already. Perhaps wash in Woolite? But I shouldn't have to. Most visible around collar. Will unlikely purchase black again, choose a lighter color if you can.
product_name: Gildan Mens DryBlend Adult T-Shirt, 2-Pack Shirt

reviews:
The collar on this shirt is noticeably smaller than standard.
Im a reasonably normal size, semi athletic guy and wear a standard medium or slim fit in every shirt - including this one. But the neck was tight - which made it uncomfortable to wear, especially outside when it's hot . The tight collar made it much hotter than it should be.

Id recommend another shirt.
product_name: Gildan Mens DryBlend Adult T-Shirt, 2-Pack Shirt

review_title: go for a size up for a better fit. Overall
reviews: A well made 2 pack of t-shirts. Keeps me cooler when the temperature gets hot outside (or inside). Sweat does bleed out but excessive sweating will just drench the t-shirt turning it into a wet towel! If you're in between sizes, go for a size up for a better fit. Overall, a decently priced, well fitted & a well stitched pair of t-shirts that will keep one reasonable cool when the temperature rises.
product_name: Gildan Mens DryBlend Adult T-Shirt, 2-Pack Shirt
